title: Nike Football: Whatever It Takes - Episode Two
description:
After graduating from The Nike Academy, Titi Accam went on to play pro in Sweden. He now plays for one of the country's top clubs. Watch his story.

Follow the Whatever It Takes series and find out how you can join the Nike Chance here:

http://go.nike.co
